al Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbKnockback Immunity<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/756879fc2f94c1df98ecd39bf3dd90ae2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases HP by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Wind) HP 60% = Critical Rate +8%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Wind: <br>increases their critical rate by 8%<br>when their HP is 60% or above.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/da5f60b4b73eaa0143835a3ec1cf809d2.png\\"><\/span><span>Rebellious Commander<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Grants the user a stack of the \\"Grand Strategist\\"<br>effect for every 10 seconds that pass without the<br>user being knocked back by an enemy.<br>Grand Strategist increases strength by 25%<br>and the chances of inflicting poison by 20%.<br>This buff can stack up to three times, but all<br>stacks will be lost upon being knocked back by<br>an enemy.<br><br>Also, using Lethal Operation will grant the user<br>a strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of two. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9d77939f4269ebb33ba6b5e2044474042.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Bog Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to bog by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted bog on them, their strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will<br>not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d5719ca16fe586e5d8cad76d24b6f2192.png\\"><\/span><span>Poisoned Punisher & Poison = Attack Rate I<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases damage to poisoned enemies by 30%<br>and, upon successfully poisoning an enemy,<br>increases the user\'s attack rate by 10% for<br>15 seconds. After activating, this attack rate<br>increase will not activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1631426400,"prev_article_id":"2453","next_article_id":"2469","image_path":"","update_time":1631087488}}}'